2015-05-19 13:04:33	--	- Quantum Thief' was nominated for the 2011 Locus Award for Best First
2015-05-19 13:04:33	--	- Novel.  Rajaniemi lives in Edinburgh, Scotland where he is founding
2015-05-19 13:04:33	--	- director of ThinkTank Maths, a commercial research organisation.
